0:02:31.907,0:02:34.407
Both of you, please have a seat.

0:02:36.007,0:02:38.407
The birds disappear in the snowy winter.

0:02:38.907,0:02:40.907
Although it's not as lively as spring,

0:02:41.207,0:02:43.107
winter has its own charm.

0:02:43.507,0:02:45.107
Indeed.

0:02:45.400,0:02:46.920
What do you think, Lady Fuca?

0:02:48.300,0:02:51.540
Your Highness invited me to appreciate
winter's beauty, so I am.

0:02:52.420,0:02:55.380
That makes me feel that I'm forcing you.

0:02:56.800,0:02:59.900
Actually, it's good to see more of each other, and talk.

0:03:00.248,0:03:03.285
In this way we'll become closer, and avoid misunderstandings and rifts.

0:03:03.507,0:03:05.307
We are brought together by serving HIs Majesty.

0:03:05.427,0:03:07.303
How could we have misunderstandings or rifts?

0:03:07.500,0:03:11.700
Winter has reminded me of a story.

0:03:12.220,0:03:15.940
Your Highness is learned and educated.
I'd like to hear it.

0:03:16.707,0:03:19.107
It's the story of "human swine."

0:03:19.407,0:03:21.607
I'm neither learned nor educated.

0:03:22.000,0:03:24.100
I don't remember the details well.

0:03:24.420,0:03:26.760
It happened during the reign of Emperor Gaozu of Han.

0:03:26.800,0:03:29.400
Lady Qi gained favor and offended Empress Lü.

0:03:29.700,0:03:32.040
After Empress Lü  became the Empress Dowager,

0:03:32.040,0:03:34.260
she cut off Lady Qi's hands and feet,

0:03:34.300,0:03:36.880
gouged her eyes, cut her ears, and used poison to make her mute.

0:03:37.100,0:03:40.060
She locked her in the outhouse.
This punishment is called "human swine".

0:03:40.400,0:03:43.300
Lady Qi was one of the most beautiful women of her time.

0:03:43.640,0:03:46.540
It's so pathetic that she ended up like that.

0:03:46.860,0:03:48.380
Empress Lü  was unbearably cruel,

0:03:48.780,0:03:52.040
but Lady Qi had only herself to blame. 

0:03:52.840,0:03:55.160
She was deluded by her favor.

0:03:55.400,0:03:59.800
Women can hold deep grudges, and Empress Lü  was no exception.

0:04:00.280,0:04:01.400
Lady Fuca,

0:04:02.720,0:04:03.580
am I right?

0:04:04.980,0:04:05.860
- Jinxi.
- My Lady!

0:04:06.080,0:04:07.720
Help Lady Fuca to her chair.

0:04:08.240,0:04:09.060
Yes.

0:04:09.200,0:04:10.600
It is only a story.

0:04:10.907,0:04:12.407
What's the matter, Fuca?

0:04:12.807,0:04:17.307
Perhaps Lady Fuca was troubled by my lack of skill.

0:04:17.807,0:04:22.207
I told it so poorly - she could not understand it.

0:04:22.600,0:04:26.000
Why did you tell me that story?

0:04:27.240,0:04:31.440
Although Consort Nian is arrogant and domineering,
I admire one of her qualities.

0:04:32.300,0:04:34.900
She is ruthless when she is determined.

0:04:36.000,0:04:38.180
In the past, someone simply made an offensive remark

0:04:38.220,0:04:40.240
and was banished to another palace.

0:04:40.580,0:04:43.600
If Consort Nian was abused on Long Street,

0:04:43.880,0:04:45.880
I wonder how she would take revenge?

0:04:46.100,0:04:49.400
If it happened to Consort Nian, given her temperament,

0:04:49.807,0:04:52.807
she would administer the human swine punishment,

0:04:53.100,0:04:55.900
or another more painful than death.

0:04:56.680,0:05:00.200
Yes, if I were more like Consort Nian,

0:05:00.600,0:05:03.780
I wouldn't have allowed myself to be
bullied after I entered the harem.

0:05:04.420,0:05:07.700
Sourire, you are greatly favored by His Majesty.

0:05:08.107,0:05:09.907
You can do anything you like.

0:05:10.200,0:05:11.980
I beg Your HIghness's forgiveness.

0:05:11.980,0:05:14.700
I admit my fault. 
I will not act like that again.

0:05:15.007,0:05:18.207
Fuca, you've always acted so sure of yourself. 
Where is this guilt coming from?

0:05:18.400,0:05:22.000
I was just telling a story.

0:05:22.800,0:05:26.200
I was listening to Consort Astuce. 
I beg Your Highness's forgiveness.

0:05:26.240,0:05:27.180
Were you?

0:05:28.000,0:05:30.900
Whatever it is, we can discuss it later.

0:05:32.320,0:05:36.140
Although Sima Qian [a historian in Han dynasty]
wrote as if dictated by Heaven,

0:05:36.260,0:05:38.940
he didn't really know what a human swine was like.

0:05:39.140,0:05:42.180
As far as I know, human swine is not the worst.

0:05:42.860,0:05:46.500
In the Tang Dynasty, concubines were made into human swine,

0:05:47.200,0:05:50.300
and then soaked in a wine cask.

0:05:50.600,0:05:52.700
This punishment was called ...

0:05:52.780,0:05:54.480
"drunken bones".

0:05:55.620,0:05:57.740
Even though it was cruel,

0:05:57.900,0:05:59.756
she should have expected it

0:05:59.900,0:06:02.320
since every action has a consequence.

0:06:12.600,0:06:14.980
My Lady, what's the matter with you?

0:06:15.360,0:06:16.560
My Lady, please wake up.

0:06:16.720,0:06:18.800
I thought she had a strong stomach,

0:06:19.060,0:06:21.760
but her boldness was hollow.

0:06:22.000,0:06:25.500
Jinxi, Lady Fuca is not feeling well. Help her back.

0:06:25.700,0:06:26.500
My Lady...

0:06:26.500,0:06:27.440
Both of you!

0:06:34.600,0:06:38.100
Come here, over here.

0:06:40.900,0:06:43.180
- Carry her away.
- Yes.

0:06:44.860,0:06:46.900
Madam, do we need to send for the imperial doctors?

0:06:46.900,0:06:49.440
Tell a doctor to visit, but don't spend too much time on her.

0:06:49.800,0:06:51.060
Yes.

0:06:59.100,0:07:01.200
"Kill the chicken to scare the monkey."

0:07:01.500,0:07:07.500
The chicken is dead now.
What does Your Highness want to tell me?

0:07:07.700,0:07:10.400
It's good to talk with an intelligent woman like you, Lady Cao.

0:07:10.560,0:07:12.240
Conversation becomes effortless.

0:07:12.320,0:07:14.220
You are not cruel or vindictive.

0:07:14.500,0:07:16.980
If Lady Fuca really offended Your Highness,

0:07:17.420,0:07:19.680
you could just send her to the Ministry of Penalty.

0:07:20.360,0:07:22.440
You didn't need to stage this trouble.

0:07:23.100,0:07:26.840
Your Highness did this to instill fear.

0:07:27.800,0:07:32.100
If Your HIghness has something to say,
please say it to me directly.

0:07:32.400,0:07:35.900
It usually takes "nine turns to reach your heart", Cao.

0:07:36.580,0:07:38.800
I am quite surprised

0:07:38.907,0:07:41.107
to be invited to be candid.

0:07:41.407,0:07:43.707
I had a cold a few days ago,

0:07:43.800,0:07:47.700
so I frequently reminded His Majesty to visit you. 
I hope you didn't mind.

0:07:48.580,0:07:51.300
I appreciated it, Your Highness.

0:07:51.807,0:07:56.607
But although His Majesty was with me,
his heart was with Your Highness

0:07:56.845,0:07:59.211
as if his soul had no home.

0:07:59.300,0:08:01.300
Lady Cao, you are intelligent.

0:08:01.300,0:08:04.000
You shouldn't worry where his heart resides.

0:08:04.379,0:08:07.062
“Seeing the person makes it harder to feel detached.”

0:08:07.407,0:08:09.807
As long as His Majesty visits you now and then,

0:08:10.107,0:08:13.707
assuredly you will gain heaven's favor
by using your clever mind.

0:08:14.024,0:08:18.130
Consort Nian's loss of favor created a burden 
for you, and affected Princess Wenyi.

0:08:18.600,0:08:22.200
His Majesty had not visited you for half a year, had he?

0:08:23.040,0:08:27.160
I'm not blessed by Heaven.
I don't expect His Majesty's attention.

0:08:27.600,0:08:29.900
It isn't a concern to be treated this way,

0:08:30.140,0:08:31.600
except for Princess Wenyi's sake.

0:08:32.020,0:08:34.600
If she isn't cherished by her father during childhood,

0:08:34.807,0:08:36.907
what will her future bring?

0:08:37.207,0:08:39.307
I was so shortsighted.

0:08:39.600,0:08:42.060
I wasn't "the smart bird that chooses a good tree to perch on".

0:08:42.100,0:08:43.900
And now am in a bleak situation.

0:08:44.200,0:08:46.860
I don't blame anyone.

0:08:48.480,0:08:50.560
You shouldn't waste time on regret.

0:08:50.720,0:08:53.540
The Princess's future depends on you fighting for her.

0:08:54.640,0:08:56.440
As for the situation in the past,

0:08:56.440,0:08:59.500
it was not shortsighted to align yourself with Consort Nian.

0:08:59.860,0:09:02.900
And it was not an easy alliance to form.

0:09:03.840,0:09:06.740
But you are still seen as closely affiliated with Consort Nian.

0:09:06.920,0:09:08.060
That's not good.

0:09:09.000,0:09:12.320
In truth, I am greatly concerned for our future.

0:09:12.980,0:09:15.780
I hope that Consort Nian's fall from grace
will not reflect on me.

0:09:17.640,0:09:19.520
Consort Nian is impetuous and ruthless.

0:09:19.980,0:09:22.280
Your days with her must have been difficult.

0:09:23.660,0:09:27.340
You knew I was innocent in the cassava starch incident.

0:09:27.660,0:09:30.540
You must have known who used Princess Wenyi to gain favor.

0:09:31.120,0:09:32.240
Poor Princess Wenyi.

0:09:32.580,0:09:34.480
It was such torture for her at that age.

0:09:35.220,0:09:36.600
It makes my heart ache.

0:09:38.040,0:09:39.160
As a mother,

0:09:39.160,0:09:41.340
seeing your own child suffer,

0:09:42.220,0:09:44.180
you must have hurt even more.

0:09:46.940,0:09:49.200
But without Consort Nian’s favor,

0:09:49.440,0:09:52.640
I wouldn't have been able to give birth to the Princess.

0:09:53.480,0:09:55.380
It was reasonable to pay her back for her aid.

0:09:55.500,0:09:56.740
But what happened afterward...

0:09:56.920,0:10:00.240
she used your child to gain favor for herself.

0:10:01.860,0:10:04.260
In fact, you are no less clever than Consort Nian.

0:10:04.920,0:10:07.560
You followed her in the past to protect yourself.

0:10:08.720,0:10:11.280
Consort Nian is domineering, and I could not defy her.

0:10:12.320,0:10:14.640
When Noble Lady Chun fell into the water,

0:10:14.880,0:10:16.940
I wanted to warn Your Highness

0:10:17.420,0:10:19.160
but it was too late to make any difference.

0:10:19.500,0:10:21.760
You have a perceptive mind, Lady Cao,

0:10:22.740,0:10:25.980
and were quick to see that Consort Nian would be unreliable.

0:10:26.400,0:10:28.500
So, you secretly did me a favor,

0:10:28.800,0:10:30.640
I am a person who repays my gratitude.

0:10:34.480,0:10:37.240
I could only obey all her orders.

0:10:37.940,0:10:41.680
I did not have the strength to act against her.

0:10:42.460,0:10:46.200
Unfortunately, Noble Lady Chun was not saved.

0:10:47.300,0:10:48.900
Now I dare to ask,

0:10:49.740,0:10:52.280
how did Noble Lady Chun lose her footing?

0:10:53.420,0:10:56.700
If you are fearful, you don't have to tell me.

0:10:59.140,0:11:02.300
Consort Nian was jealous that Lady Chun
was favored at such a young age

0:11:02.700,0:11:04.240
and was close to Your Highness.

0:11:04.420,0:11:06.860
She was eager to cut off Your Highness's wings.

0:11:07.260,0:11:09.080
She was that impatient?

0:11:09.920,0:11:11.740
She wasn't afraid that His Majesty would investigate?

0:11:12.360,0:11:13.920
Consort Nian sees everyone else as beneath her;

0:11:14.340,0:11:16.240
killing a concubine meant nothing to her.

0:11:16.780,0:11:19.680
Besides, her death left no trace of a suspect.

0:11:20.620,0:11:22.760
When Lady Chun looked for her kite, she overheard

0:11:22.860,0:11:26.660
a private meeting between Consort Nian
and General Nian’s subordinate.

0:11:27.040,0:11:29.580
That's why she was silenced by Consort Nian.

0:11:29.960,0:11:33.000
It is reasonable that Consort Nian wanted
to meet General Nian’s subordinate.

0:11:33.720,0:11:35.540
Why would they need to meet secretly?

0:11:36.200,0:11:37.680
Consort Nian's expenditures are very high

0:11:38.320,0:11:40.340
but her money is not unlimited.

0:11:41.060,0:11:42.520
To increase her income,

0:11:43.160,0:11:47.360
she passed on the names of those who wished to 
buy an official position to General Nian.

0:11:48.200,0:11:53.040
Zhao Zhiyuan was re-appointed to 
another position by bribing Consort Nian.

0:11:53.280,0:11:57.540
How dare she collude with Nian Gengyao 
to influence the official appointments in court?

0:11:57.680,0:12:02.960
And now, these corrupt officials have formed 
a faction supporting Nian Genyao.

0:12:04.080,0:12:06.460
You had no choice in being my enemy in the past.

0:12:06.700,0:12:07.920
it’s understandable.

0:12:08.480,0:12:11.020
Giving birth to Princess Wenyi is a great 
contribution to the imperial family.

0:12:11.340,0:12:13.380
But after years of supporting Consort Nian,

0:12:13.920,0:12:17.220
you were not even on par with
Concubine Beauté who was childless.

0:12:17.620,0:12:19.000
It's pitiful.

0:12:20.580,0:12:24.380
A mother’s status impacts her child’s future.

0:12:25.320,0:12:28.380
Perhaps you do not know.
His Majesty told me only yesterday.

0:12:28.700,0:12:34.300
Yingge Khagan was violently murdered less than half a
month after Princess Zhaogui was married to him.

0:12:35.460,0:12:38.160
Now that the Princess is widowed, will she return soon?

0:12:38.660,0:12:40.800
It would be her blessing to return.

0:12:41.480,0:12:48.020
The Princess has to follow the
local custom and marry the new khagan.

0:12:48.460,0:12:50.640
How could this humiliation happen to the Princess?

0:12:50.640,0:12:52.740
A woman's sole duty is to continue the family lineage.

0:12:53.200,0:12:56.260
Even though unwilling, she has to follow their custom.

0:12:56.760,0:13:00.480
Falling from a primary wife to a concubine.

0:13:17.400,0:13:20.160
I will render my humble service to Your Highness!

0:13:20.680,0:13:22.820
I beg Your Highness to protect Princess Wenyi and myself.

0:13:23.180,0:13:24.780
I will be infinitely grateful.

0:13:29.200,0:13:32.280
I have long admired you, Lady Cao.

0:13:32.640,0:13:34.580
Today, we have become close.

0:13:35.080,0:13:36.900
It is more than I wished for.

0:13:42.380,0:13:44.000
If you feel cold, My Lady,

0:13:44.000,0:13:45.480
you can lie down in bed.

0:13:45.860,0:13:47.840
I will fill a hot water bottle for you.

0:13:47.840,0:13:48.740
Coua,

0:13:50.000,0:13:53.560
do you think that others are laughing at me now?

0:13:54.580,0:13:56.360
My Lady, you are overthinking.

0:13:57.060,0:13:59.700
When I was in high favor,

0:14:01.200,0:14:05.280
people were grinding their teeth with resentment.

0:14:06.120,0:14:09.420
But now, Concubine Sourire has silently stolen my favor

0:14:09.980,0:14:13.880
and never treats me the same way as before.

0:14:14.480,0:14:16.280
How could people not laugh at me?

0:14:16.660,0:14:19.200
His Majesty has only summoned her a few more times.

0:14:19.840,0:14:21.360
His Majesty has not forgotten you, My Lady.

0:14:21.460,0:14:22.320
Really?

0:14:23.240,0:14:26.680
His Majesty always said that my voice is soft and delicate.

0:14:27.320,0:14:31.860
But now that His Majesty is with Concubine Sourire, 
he has forgotten everything else.

0:14:39.480,0:14:41.400
Without nose, without ears.

0:14:42.620,0:14:45.300
Without hands, without feet.

0:14:52.240,0:14:53.740
What’s going on, Fuca?

0:14:55.420,0:14:56.700
I don't want to be a human swine.

0:14:56.760,0:14:58.400
- Human swine?
- I don't want to be a human swine.

0:14:58.600,0:14:59.960
Who would do that?

0:15:00.460,0:15:02.800
She wants to make me into a human swine!

0:15:02.800,0:15:04.860
- It’s impossible. 
- Your Highness, help!

0:15:04.980,0:15:06.680
- No one would dare! 
- I don't want to be a human swine!

0:15:06.680,0:15:07.880
No one would!

0:15:08.200,0:15:09.160
You!

0:15:09.720,0:15:10.920
What has happened to Lady Fuca?

0:15:11.020,0:15:12.400
I'm not sure, Your Highness.

0:15:12.480,0:15:14.860
A few days ago, My Lady had a talk with
Concubine Sourire and Lady Cao.

0:15:15.220,0:15:19.600
She fainted in the pavilion and has been
like this ever since she was revived.

0:15:22.080,0:15:23.260
Concubine Sourire ...

0:15:23.820,0:15:25.400
Concubine Sourire threatened her?

0:15:25.420,0:15:27.620
It makes no sense ...

0:15:28.440,0:15:29.700
Lady Cao was there as well.

0:15:30.020,0:15:31.440
But she didn’t have such a shock.

0:15:33.920,0:15:35.360
I don't want to become a human swine!

0:15:35.660,0:15:37.120
I don't want to become a human swine!

0:15:48.720,0:15:51.860
My Lady, Lady Fuca has lost her mind.

0:15:52.920,0:15:57.020
I heard Lady Fuca became insane and started to
talk incoherently after recovering.

0:15:57.680,0:16:00.380
She is afraid to go out and has been hiding in bed.

0:16:01.400,0:16:03.680
- Does His Majesty know of this?
- Yes.

0:16:04.200,0:16:06.300
Lady Fuca has disrupted the peace of the palace.

0:16:06.300,0:16:10.720
His Majesty has placed an order
confining Lady Fuca to her palace

0:16:11.100,0:16:13.620
and has only sent a few imperial doctors to treat her.

0:16:16.200,0:16:17.660
I thought she was strong.

0:16:17.900,0:16:20.080
But just a few words scared away her sanity?

0:16:21.000,0:16:24.060
She has a guilty conscience,
and her own fear has driven her insane.

0:16:25.940,0:16:29.980
Since His Majesty has sent doctors, they will treat her.

0:16:44.440,0:16:46.100
- Go knock on the door.
- Yes.

0:16:58.320,0:17:01.820
My Lady, Consort Astuce is here
and needs to see you urgently.

0:17:02.280,0:17:06.780
It's rather strange since Consort Astuce never visits us. 
Why would she come today?

0:17:06.980,0:17:08.540
I don't have time to see her.

0:17:09.160,0:17:12.800
Go tell her she will not be involved
in what happened to Lady Fuca.

