Please.

0:33:32.465,0:33:33.735
This tea is called "snow-drop jade".

0:33:34.225,0:33:35.735
It just arrived on the fastest courier.

0:33:36.260,0:33:38.500
Please try some and see
if it's deserving of Your Ladyship's liking.

0:33:46.380,0:33:48.520
Your Highness holds His Majesty's highest favor in the palace.

0:33:48.780,0:33:50.760
Naturally, Your Highness has the best of everything.

0:33:51.140,0:33:53.260
When I had my miscarriage,

0:33:53.934,0:33:56.243
Your Ladyship were the only one to visit me, despite my status.

0:33:56.920,0:33:58.580
I will always remember that.

0:33:58.980,0:34:02.940
I hope a day comes when I can repay Your Ladyship
for your heart-warming kindness.

0:34:03.260,0:34:05.800
Will Your Highness put in a word to His Majesty for me?

0:34:07.920,0:34:09.560
If I were you,

0:34:10.185,0:34:12.815
I would accept His Majesty's decree.

0:34:13.380,0:34:15.120
Let Empress Dowager take care of the princess.

0:34:17.260,0:34:19.120
Why does Your Highness say so?

0:34:21.180,0:34:23.060
As both a wife and a mother,

0:34:23.465,0:34:26.370
of course Your Ladyship must always
think of your husband and children,

0:34:26.479,0:34:27.754
and place their interests above your own.

0:34:27.820,0:34:29.460
Wouldn't Your Ladyship agree?

0:34:30.860,0:34:33.060
Prince Dun attacked a court official a few days ago,

0:34:33.400,0:34:35.140
and caused an uproar among the other officials.

0:34:35.340,0:34:39.260
Hopefully Prince Dun will consider
visiting Zhang Lin and apologizing to him.

0:34:40.740,0:34:42.160
With a temper like his,

0:34:42.260,0:34:45.780
he would never apologize to someone else.

0:34:45.940,0:34:47.300
If Your Ladyship cares for Prince Dun,

0:34:47.600,0:34:50.040
you must try and persuade him.

0:34:51.300,0:34:53.320
His Majesty wants to shield Prince Dun,

0:34:53.620,0:34:55.540
but ultimately it is Prince Dun who was at fault.

0:34:55.940,0:34:58.740
Zhang Lin is still unable to get out of bed.

0:34:59.860,0:35:01.680
His Majesty is upset, after all.

0:35:02.560,0:35:06.080
Prince Dun has a straightforward nature
and may stir up tensions again in the future.

0:35:07.164,0:35:10.678
If the princess is in the palace, she will be able to
speak to His Majesty in times of strife.

0:35:11.100,0:35:12.400
Wouldn't that be a good thing?

0:35:12.740,0:35:14.240
I will also suggest to His Majesty

0:35:14.785,0:35:17.975
that you be allowed to come to the palace
frequently to visit the princess.

0:35:18.580,0:35:19.980
What does Your Ladyship think?

0:35:22.540,0:35:25.420
Since His Majesty has put so much thought into this,

0:35:26.020,0:35:29.100
His Lordship and I cannot refuse his grace.

0:35:30.260,0:35:31.360
I thank Your Highness.

0:35:34.420,0:35:35.740
Please, have some tea.

0:35:40.240,0:35:42.300
I've finally learned

0:35:43.040,0:35:44.780
what it means to "anxiously await
something until one's eyes hurt".

0:35:46.220,0:35:48.360
Your Highness, please don't say that.

0:35:51.120,0:35:53.060
I wonder when

0:35:54.220,0:35:56.260
I will be able to see His Majesty again.

0:35:57.040,0:35:58.280
Your Highness need not worry.

0:35:58.320,0:36:00.460
Great General Nian has sent a messenger.

0:36:00.900,0:36:03.140
He is aware that Your Highness has been treated coldly recently,

0:36:03.240,0:36:06.780
and has made plans with State Prince Dun
to probe His Majesty's affections toward Your Highness.

0:36:07.360,0:36:08.860
I have already told you

0:36:09.180,0:36:11.360
not to bring this up with my brother.

0:36:12.500,0:36:14.500
Even if we were not to raise it with him

0:36:15.320,0:36:19.080
everyone in the palace knows how His Majesty
is treating Your Highness right now.

0:36:19.560,0:36:21.460
How could the Great General be unaware?

0:36:23.540,0:36:25.200
Out of all the things he could have done,

0:36:25.400,0:36:27.580
why did he choose to once again side with State Prince Dun?

0:36:28.200,0:36:30.640
He may owe Prince Dun some favors,

0:36:31.540,0:36:33.600
but they shouldn't be in overly close contact.

0:36:34.020,0:36:36.060
Now that Prince Dun's daughter has been
promoted to the second rank

0:36:36.220,0:36:37.600
and his son the fourth rank.

0:36:37.740,0:36:39.040
His Lordship is in high favor

0:36:39.320,0:36:43.020
and it's only natural that the Great General
would see him more frequently.

0:36:43.400,0:36:46.720
State Prince Dun is known for his
short temper and domineering attitude.

0:36:47.840,0:36:50.880
The Great General has ordered me to
ease Your Highness's worries.

0:36:51.740,0:36:54.420
General Nian said he only needs to do one thing for His Lordship

0:36:54.940,0:36:59.040
and then His Lordship will help Your Highness
 regain His Majesty's favor.

0:37:00.740,0:37:01.740
Really?

0:37:01.900,0:37:03.420
With the Great General and His Lordship on your side,

0:37:03.660,0:37:05.460
there's nothing for Your Highness to worry about.

0:37:07.040,0:37:08.340
I do hope so.

0:37:12.080,0:37:13.520
- Song Zhi.
- Yes.

0:37:13.740,0:37:15.380
Light my Pleasancy for me.

0:37:16.520,0:37:18.780
It puts my mind at ease.

0:37:20.260,0:37:21.200
Yes.

0:37:21.600,0:37:23.160
His Majesty the Emperor.

0:37:23.620,0:37:25.900
- Peace and grace to Your Majesty.
- Rise.

0:37:31.740,0:37:35.660
Yesterday, State Prince Dun apologized to Zhang Lin in person.

0:37:36.540,0:37:38.020
Although it wasn't much of an apology

0:37:38.380,0:37:40.620
at least things have quieted down somewhat.

0:37:41.300,0:37:43.900
Huan Huan, you were of great help.

0:37:45.220,0:37:47.680
It is my duty to allay Your Majesty's worries.

0:37:49.940,0:37:52.620
I don't understand politics and can't help you in court affairs.

0:37:53.360,0:37:56.240
I can only chime in on small family matters.

0:38:02.320,0:38:04.520
This "snow-drop jade" is certainly excellent tea.

0:38:05.480,0:38:08.460
I know you like it so I sent the best to your palace.

0:38:08.880,0:38:10.080
Is it to your liking?

0:38:10.200,0:38:11.520
Of course.

0:38:12.260,0:38:15.300
I offered it to State Prince Dun's wife when she visited

0:38:16.020,0:38:18.380
but it didn't seem novel to Her Ladyship.

0:38:19.340,0:38:22.940
It was fortunate that Her Ladyship
didn't mind the tea and my hospitality.

0:38:24.220,0:38:27.540
Whatever tribute offerings the palace receives

0:38:28.160,0:38:31.040
Great General Nian has the same, if not better.

0:38:31.840,0:38:34.140
Now, even State Prince Dun has the same.

0:38:34.880,0:38:36.580
I never granted him that tea.

0:38:37.480,0:38:39.240
Where could he have gotten it?

0:38:41.120,0:38:42.860
Your Majesty need not be angry.

0:38:43.460,0:38:45.760
His assault of a civil official has raised "surging waves of chaos".

0:38:46.160,0:38:48.540
If any more gossip spreads after the waves calm,

0:38:49.080,0:38:50.980
it will tarnish his military achievements.

0:38:51.340,0:38:52.920
Does Your Majesty agree?

0:39:02.020,0:39:04.120
Your Majesty, I have brought you some water.

0:39:14.320,0:39:15.360
Your Majesty,

0:39:15.800,0:39:19.040
I've made a new sachet to present to Your Majesty.

0:39:20.020,0:39:22.400
Does Your Majesty like it?

0:39:23.520,0:39:27.340
Huan Huan made me a sachet a few days ago.

0:39:28.800,0:39:30.380
And I have it with me right now.

0:39:31.940,0:39:33.680
Having another would be unnecessary.

0:39:34.660,0:39:37.300
My needlework cannot compare to Sourire's.

0:39:37.840,0:39:38.940
Don't be foolish!

0:39:38.940,0:39:41.200
Lingrong's skills are far superior to my own.

0:39:42.080,0:39:46.100
His Majesty's belt and fan tassel

0:39:46.860,0:39:48.280
are both made by your hand.

0:39:48.700,0:39:50.120
That truly attests to your skill.

0:39:50.780,0:39:53.200
That's just because His Majesty
doesn't mind my coarse handwork.

0:39:58.280,0:40:00.640
This one is also good. I like it.

0:40:01.240,0:40:03.260
Ask Madam Orchid to put it in my sleep chamber.

0:40:04.100,0:40:05.860
My work is clumsy and inept,

0:40:05.860,0:40:09.320
I am glad as long as Your Majesty
appreciates the thought that went into it

0:40:12.860,0:40:14.360
The sachet Sourire made

0:40:14.560,0:40:16.540
suits Your Majesty's noble temperament.

0:40:17.560,0:40:20.540
The one I presented, however, looks unsophisticated.

0:40:21.480,0:40:23.180
I hope Your Majesty will pardon me.

0:40:24.140,0:40:26.260
There's nothing unsophisticated about it.

0:40:27.480,0:40:28.880
I understand the thought you put into it.

0:40:29.440,0:40:31.320
There's no need to ask for my pardon.

0:40:34.940,0:40:36.940
Sourire, your sewing and embroidery is getting even better.

0:40:37.660,0:40:40.680
If you make a sachet with a pair of mandarin ducks,

0:40:41.100,0:40:43.180
it will show your tender affection towards His Majesty.

0:40:43.540,0:40:46.000
His Majesty might like it even more.

0:40:46.620,0:40:48.080
That would be very thoughtful.

0:40:48.500,0:40:50.980
But if His Majesty goes about wearing the sachet day and night,

0:40:51.240,0:40:52.840
it will look overly sentimental.

0:40:53.600,0:40:56.120
Wearing a dragon sachet instead shows
His Majesty's heavenly authority.

0:40:56.400,0:40:58.280
But speaking of mandarin duck sachets,

0:40:59.060,0:41:01.340
I can make one for you if you like, Si Lang,

0:41:01.900,0:41:03.460
to put under your pillow.

0:41:05.140,0:41:06.340
What are you writing out?

0:41:06.700,0:41:09.120
The lyrical poem by Liu Yong
using the metre of "Rain Sounded Bell".

0:41:10.060,0:41:14.120
I like your calligraphy, but Liu Yong's poems are sorrowful.

0:41:15.300,0:41:19.380
“Hands held, gazing into each other's teary eyes,
Our sobbing breath chokes the words to be said.”

0:41:19.580,0:41:21.280
That poem does not match the present moment.

0:41:42.760,0:41:47.920
“This night brings a full moon and blooming flowers.
May My beloved and I long abide in this peaceful life.”

0:41:48.040,0:41:50.060
Here, take this and put it above your bed.

0:41:50.300,0:41:51.720
I thank Your Majesty.

0:41:52.680,0:41:54.820
Your Majesty is so affectionate towards Sourire.

0:41:55.040,0:41:56.580
This is a romantic story for the ages.

0:41:56.760,0:42:00.140
No one could ever enjoy such fortune as you, Sourire.

0:42:01.000,0:42:02.620
Your Majesty needs to make peace with Lingrong.

0:42:02.960,0:42:04.780
She's being silly and "sour as vinegar".

0:42:05.300,0:42:06.860
You always tease me, Sourire.

0:42:07.280,0:42:09.980
How would I dare to be sour about you and His Majesty?

0:42:10.220,0:42:11.680
Lingong is the mildest of all of you.

0:42:12.460,0:42:14.000
If she's as sour as vinegar,

0:42:14.000,0:42:16.220
it's vinegar that has only been fermenting for a month

0:42:16.460,0:42:17.740
which is barely sour at all.

